  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Orthopedic Implant Stress Prediction Credibility Assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for finite element analysis (FEA) prediction of peak von Mises stress in a tibial tray component of a total knee replacement system under physiological loading conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict relative stress distributions sufficient to support design comparison decisions at Model Risk Level 3. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels for MRL 3. Decision: Accepted.",
